<TestCaseEntity>
   <description>When a user applies a filter

Then the system shall:

Display the applied filters in the order they were selected
Each applied-filter-tab must provide the ability to remove the applied-filter
Applied filters will only display when the user changes a filter from its default setting
if desktop:
The applied-filter-tabs will wrap to a new line when they reach the end of the device-viewport
if mobile:
The applied-filters-tabs will be in-line with one another
Applied-filter-tabs will be in a swipeable carousel</description>
